<p>I am working with php, and made this little function to only return an array with the same month, but I need this to be returned in order of day too, I tried to use sort, usort and neither worked out.</p>
<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$jsonFile</span>     = <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">file_get_contents</span>(BASE_TEMPLATE . <span class="hljs-string">'/templates/json/'</span> . AMBIENTE . <span class="hljs-string">'/'</span> . <span class="hljs-string">'demo_birthday'</span> . <span class="hljs-string">'-data.json'</span>);
<span class="hljs-variable">$jsonData</span>     = <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">json_decode</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$jsonFile</span>);
</code></pre>
