    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>Given what you show with print_r you can either use array_multisort:</p>
<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$values</span> = <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">getBirthdayMonth</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$actualMonth</span>, <span class="hljs-variable">$slide</span>, <span class="hljs-variable">$arrayMonth</span>);
<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">array_multisort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$values</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">// The default options work for your case</span>
</code></pre>
<p>Or usort like you said:</p>
<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$values</span> = <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">getBirthdayMonth</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$actualMonth</span>, <span class="hljs-variable">$slide</span>, <span class="hljs-variable">$arrayMonth</span>);
<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">cmp</span>(<span class="hljs-params"><span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>, <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span></span>)
</span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] == <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]) {
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
    }
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (<span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] &lt; <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]) ? -<span class="hljs-number">1</span> : <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;
}

<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">usort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$values</span>, <span class="hljs-string">"cmp"</span>);

<span class="hljs-comment">//Or even shorter:</span>
<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">usort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$values</span>, function (<span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>, <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>) {
  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">gmp_sign</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] - <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]);
}); 
</code></pre>
    </div>
